profile:
Green Side Up Contracting Inc. is a professional member of Landscape Ontario & we are an authorized TrexPro - Platinum status!

Over the last 22 years, we have established ourselves within the construction industry as an honest and reputable contractor.  We have earned this reputation by shaping the company around four core values: honesty, transparency, quality of workmanship, backed by above industry-standard warranties!

As the President of Green Side Up Contracting Inc. and a board member of the Toronto Chapter of Landscape Ontario, PROTECTING YOUR INVESTMENT and delivering EXCELLENCE are two of Jay's key priorities.

         ****************************10 YEAR STRUCTURAL WARRANTY - FENCING ****************************

Green Side Up Contracting Inc is a consistent award-winning, construction company that focuses on delivering high-quality workmanship and superior customer service.  We put our trust into our clients with extremely favorable payment terms - pay when the job is completed! We are active members of our community and believe in helping those who are less fortunate.

Services provided include but are not limited to:

-> Fence Construction (80' linear feet minumum)
 
-> Interlocking & Landscape Construction

-> Deck Construction (200 sq foot minumim) 

    - Trex
    - Cedar

***

Not only does Green Side Up Contracting Inc focus on PROTECTING YOUR INVESTMENT by offering a TEN-YEAR structural WARRANTY on fencing, we also believe that doing business together should be simple and transparent.

***

Please use our SELF SERVE CALCULATORS to obtain an INSTANT ESTIMATE for your DECK, FENCE or INTERLOCK project:

FENCE CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/fence-building-calculator/

DECK CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/deck-calculator/

INTERLOCKING CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/interlock-cost-calculator/

***

Please be sure to check our work by visiting:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/greensideupcontracting/

YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRNuc7PofUOEHCwMf7NdUzQ/videos?view_as=subscriber

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/GreenSideUpContracting/

We would also invite you to come on site during the construction process, so you can see our work in progress!

***

Building is fun, business is great, people are terrific and life is wonderful! 

I ask that you put your trust into Green Side Up Contracting - we not disappoint!!

On your side,

Jay Saveall

www.greensideupcontracting.com

profile:
Chase Contracting and Home Improvements is a fully licensed and insured contracting company serving the GTA. Chase is a certified Red Seal Carpenter with 16 years experience in all aspects of the renovation and building industry. Chase started as a Carpenter's apprentice in 2005. After years of working on his craft he completed his apprenticeship and became a journeyman carpenter, later achieving the honor of become a certified Red Seal Carpenter. 

After that Chase moved on to successfully work with some of the biggest leaders in the construction industry as a carpentry crew foreman in Toronto. Chase's passion drew him to a different market as he wanted to be closer to home.  He wanted to offer his skills and work for the people and families directly in the community. That is when the leap was made and Chase Contracting and Home Improvements was founded in 2017!   What sets us apart other then our skills is that we are a family run company. We truly care about our clients and our work. You are not just an invoice number when you deal with us! Either Chase himself, or Shannon, the Business Manager, are always available for any questions you may have. 

When it comes to your home, don't mess with the rest, trust the best!  We pride our ourselves on doing only top quality work at fair honest prices. Full 10 year warranty on all work. Your Satisfaction guaranteed! Check out our galleries to see some of our work!

profile:
DECKS,
We customize decks from start to finish. everything from railings to stairs with superb design. Get the modern look of composite decking or maybe cedar for a sophisticated feel. Anything you picture is always possible. customer satisfaction is what keeps us going!

FENCES,
All fences have the ability to be made with a unique personal touch, the customer can be the designer. Let us know what you want and JWC Construction has the tools to perfect it. They can be used to keep the dog in the yard, block your house from the road, or maybe to add a little privacy to your new deck!

RENOVATIONS,
Have you ever just sat down and wondered what that wall would look a different colour, or maybe how much more you could do in there if it was that much bigger. JWC cares about the love of a home and takes pride in experimenting different ways to make it your own. Anything from granite countertops for a spectacular kitchen to a finished basement to fit the pool table!

DEMO SERVICES, 
Do you have a structure or items that need to be dismantled or demolished and taken away? Are you looking for a demolition company that is fully licensed, experienced and insured? JWC Construction has what you are looking for! We are experienced in all sorts of demolition and our fully equipped friendly crew will demolish and dismantle, then take your junk away! for recycling or disposal. No mess left behind!

JUNK REMOVAL,
JWC Construction is your trust worthy full-service junk removal company. We offer junk removal services for your home and business. We ensure that your junk is recycled, donated and disposed of correctly and in a timely fashion.
Do you have old furniture, appliances, electronics, tires, construction debris, or yard waste you need to rid yourself of? JWC Construction can remove almost any material! while you relax. Weâ€™ll remove your junk and vow that no junk will be left behind! 

AGGREGATE DELIVERIES,
Don't have the time or energy to pick it up yourself? No worries! leave to us!! We deliver everything from soil, mulch, and aggregates to decorative stones. Not sure if we deliver what you are looking for? chances are we do and if we haven't we will! We'll deliver to your front door! Our friendly and knowledgeable crew are always ready to help you make your projects a reality!

HANDYMAN SERVICES,

Offering clients the best quality fences at unbeatable prices with the fastest installation times in Ontario. We offer fence installations in the regions of GTA, Toronto, Mississauga, Scarborough, Markham, Vaughan, Richmond Hill, Newmarket, King City, Bradford, Brampton, Oakville, Oshawa, Bradford etc. Our aim is to provide modern, and innovative fence designs at the lowest prices. There are no wooden products involved in the manufacturing or during installation of Mr. Fencee fences. More importantly, Mr. Fencee Fences are made in Canada, made for Canada, withstanding the most severe weather conditions and up to 147km/hr winds.
